# FANMOD Installation Guide  
### RTX 2080 ASUS OC Edition

Welcome to the step-by-step installation tutorial for setting up the FANMOD on the ASUS RTX 2080 OC Edition graphics card. This guide will walk you through each stage of the process with images and brief descriptions to ensure a smooth installation.

---

## Step-by-Step Instructions

### Step 1: Preparation  
![Step 1](https://via.placeholder.com/600x300.png?text=Step+1+Image)  
Begin by powering down your PC and removing the graphics card from the case. Make sure you’re working on a static-free surface.

---

### Step 2: Remove Existing Shroud  
![Step 2](https://via.placeholder.com/600x300.png?text=Step+2+Image)  
Carefully unscrew and detach the stock cooler or shroud from the GPU without damaging the PCB.

---

### Step 3: Clean the Surface  
![Step 3](https://via.placeholder.com/600x300.png?text=Step+3+Image)  
Wipe down the GPU surface with isopropyl alcohol to remove thermal paste and dust.

---

### Step 4: Align FANMOD Brackets  
![Step 4](https://via.placeholder.com/600x300.png?text=Step+4+Image)  
Place the FANMOD universal mounting brackets on the GPU’s existing mounting points and ensure proper alignment.

---

### Step 5: Attach Cooling Fans  
![Step 5](https://via.placeholder.com/600x300.png?text=Step+5+Image)  
Secure the 120MM cooling fans to the brackets. Ensure cables are facing outward for clean cable management.

---

### Step 6: Connect RGB Header  
![Step 6](https://via.placeholder.com/600x300.png?text=Step+6+Image)  
Plug the FANMOD RGB connector into your motherboard or RGB controller.

---

### Step 7: Apply Thermal Pads/Paste  
![Step 7](https://via.placeholder.com/600x300.png?text=Step+7+Image)  
Apply new thermal paste to the GPU chip and thermal pads to memory modules or VRMs if required.

---

### Step 8: Reinstall the GPU  
![Step 8](https://via.placeholder.com/600x300.png?text=Step+8+Image)  
Place the GPU back into your PC’s PCIe slot and reconnect power cables securely.

---

### Step 9: Attach Magnetic Skins  
![Step 9](https://via.placeholder.com/600x300.png?text=Step+9+Image)  
Snap on your desired magnetic decal skin to customize the look of your graphics card.

---

### Step 10: Power On & Test  
![Step 10](https://via.placeholder.com/600x300.png?text=Step+10+Image)  
Power on your PC, verify fan and RGB functionality, and monitor GPU temps to confirm proper installation.

---

## ✅ Installation Complete  
You’ve successfully installed FANMOD on your RTX 2080 ASUS OC Edition! Enjoy improved cooling, custom looks, and RGB flair.

---
